m.  He logged before payment.<br><br>I learned afterward that this is not the first time Srir has weaseled out of agreed-upon payment for services rendered.  Srir's word is No Good.  If you take it, you deserve what you get.<br><br>I didn't have this warning and got screwed out of time and hunting.<br><br>Again, his name is Srir (Stupid little short name but easy to remember!)<br>He is a 28th season Vah Shir Beastlord<br>He was last seen this afternoon in Greater Faydark<br>He likes to hunt in Sol A.<br>He likes to promise things to people he has no intention of ever delivering.<br><br>Pretty bad form for a supposedly &quot;Good&quot; character, don't you think?  I know EVIL characters who behave better than this clown.<br><br>You Have Been Warned.<br><br> <p><img src="http://www.datazap.net/free/feylin/images/omi/Omi3.gif"><p>"Bringing the Peace of Quellious to the Clan's enemies -- One peaceful corpse at a time."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ucrashieg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>CrashieG</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 129<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/14/02 3:45:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=999.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_supermad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Beware Srir's Promises!</span><hr size=1> bleh help people for reasons other than profit and you wont have this problem<br> <p><center><a href="http://www.graphicfreedom.com/eq/Movie1.html" window="new"><img src="http://www.graphicfreedom.com/eq/calvinnew.jpg" border="0"></a><BR><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=153879"><B>Calvin</b></a>GrandMaster FV - Resolution<BR><B>Hobbes</b><BR>Oracle FV - Resolution<font color=b