n class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Beware Srir's Promises!</span><hr size=1> Its not just once. I've heard things about this Srir person before, mostly in GFay. I've only grouped with him once and that was in High Keep. He didn't say much, but he kept fearing the mobs out of the room we were in, and didn't respond when we asked him why. Kept pouncing (pardon the pun) on every kill, then after the third time fearing and us asking why, he announced he had to leave. <br><br>He had a guild-tag on. Maybe appeal to his guildleader? <br><br>I agree its a rotten thing to do to promise payment, then reneg on the deal. I'll remember him if he asks for a rez and offers payment. <br><br> <p>Quianna Starthunder, Followers of the Stars<br>Cleric of Rodcet Nife, 26 Secrets revealed.<br> "My God... Its full of stars..."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uwhimsyprankster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>whimsy prankster</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/15/02 10:47:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=999.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Beware Srir's Promises!</span><hr size=1> He's a pud.<br><br>A complete total jerk-weed.<br><br>My knickname for him is 'Sand-Shitter'<br><br>He's a lying coward to boot.<br><br>Scum of the earth actually...in fact I cannot wait until I here him begging for another CR so I can laugh in his face, or even better drag his dead body DEEPER into the dungeon.<br><br>At level 19 he promised me and a guy I was grouping with 100 plat to go help him get his body back in 'Lavastorm'.  I figured he's 