ot;<br><br>Qnewu, Cards and I in tells knowing just knowing that he's probably going to rip us off...but thinking what the heck we'll stick it out.<br><br>Zone to FP, he says, whats the quickest way back to the moon?  Ummm, duh get to spires...maybe the ones in G Fay are closer if you catch the boat...<br><br>We goto the bank, Cards follows him to the docks, where he LDs and disappears...<br><br>Now if the Fucker had asked for help straight up and not offered any payment I would have gone anyway...Whimsy is just about chaotic enough to do that, and dying only means she gets to hear a new joke from Bristlebane anyway...but not only did he promise cash up front, he lied about the difficulty and then INTENTIONALLY tried to fuck over us with faction hits to get us to leave...Halflings don't 'aggro' on you accidentally...especially green ones...<br><br>It gets a bit better...<br><br>WK Spires:<br><br>Run up and there is Srir the sand shitter with the group of peeps heading to the Moon...I /rude him, start jawing on his lack of all things important (brains, brawn, friends, ability not to get killed...etc...)  He says:<br><br>&quot;Sorry, I just bought this character from my friend&quot;<br><br>Yeah, total BS as he was defensive before we started talking...<br><br>&quot;Sorry I have 30 plat on me, does that cover what I owe you?&quot;<br><br>At this point I decide to lay it on him...What you owe me you sack is the chance to come by and see you beg and plead for help sometime in the future and everyone around you to say, &quot;No&quot;.  You owe me a few hours of being my slave and running through a deep fuckin dungeon where everything cons RED for my amusement...thats what you 'Owe' me...<br><br>Anyway, he's scum, don't help him even for free.  Hell I'd pay you NOT to help him, just so he can suffer...and I'm normally such a nice Half-Elf...must be this Mask of Deception I keep putting on...<br><br>MODS sorry if you need to edit this post and/or w